{"id":"ahiam","term":"Ahiam","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Mother’s brother, one of David’s thirty heroes (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 23:33\">2 Sam. 23:33</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 11:35\">1 Chr. 11:35</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Samuel 23:33","1 Chronicles 11:35"]}